# Learning curriculum: raw third-party repos cloned by
# scripts/sync-learning-sources.mjs. Never commit these — they're large,
# have their own nested .git, and CareerVivid's own curriculum content lives
# in docs/learning/ and data/learning/ instead. The LICENSES we copy out of
# them stay tracked for compliance record-keeping.
third_party/learning-sources/*/
!third_party/learning-sources/LICENSES/
